hed in  1855 , but has not been much used since the early decades of the 20th century."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Maud was born in 1130. She married Adam de Weston in 1169. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1130–":"1130–Surnud","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–Surnud","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey, England":"Merton, Surrey, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1130–":"1130–Kuollut","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–Kuollut","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey, England":"Merton, Surrey, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1130–":"1130–Décédée","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–Décédée","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey, England":"Merton, Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Maud est née en 1130. Elle a épousé Adam de Weston en 1169. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"1130–":"1130–Verstorben","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–Verstorben","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey, England":"Merton, Surrey, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Maud wurde 1130 geboren. Sie hat 1169 Adam de Weston geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1130–":"1130–Desede","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–Desede","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey, England":"Merton, Surrey, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1130–":"1130–elhunyt","1151–1205":"1151–1205","1170–1242":"1170–1242","1130–Female":"1130–elhunyt","1205":"1205","1169":"1169","1242":"1242","1130":"1130","1151":"1151","1170":"1170","Merton, Merton, Surrey